item.title: CVE-2024-1088|2024-03-05T01:56:01.564Z -- rajkakadiya -- Password Protected Store for WooCommerce
item.description: The Password Protected Store for WooCommerce plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to Sensitive Information Exposure in all versions up to, and including, 1.9 via the REST API. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attackers to extract sensitive data including post titles and content.
